south african gold hold rise in march south african gold hold rose 172.56 mln rand to 4.17 billion rand in march after rise 39 mln rand to 4.0 billion rand in februari , reserv bank figur show . in volum term gold hold rose to 5.51 mln ounc in march from 5.26 mln ounc in februari , valu at 757.24 rand an ounc for march versu 754.59 rand an ounc for februari . total gold and foreign asset rose to 6.30 billion rand from 6.22 billion , of which the gold content increa to 66.22 pct from 64.3 pct . foreign bill remain at zero in march while invest fell slightli to 105.69 mln rand from februari 's 106.56 mln rand and other asset to 2.02 billion rand from 2.11 billion , the figur show . total liabil fell to 12.21 billion rand in march after rise to 13.62 billion in februari .